    <timeout>1800</timeout>

    <name>MOIN: Support of IDE Deployment Scenario. All major flows offered by the MOIN API in the area of MOF/JMI, Queries, Events, OCL, Commands, Connections/Sessions, Partitions, Refresh, Text verticalization etc. - Impl. consumer: MIE, ESM, Galaxy IDE, Mass configuration [Test Suite ID: NWDS_MOIN_001]</name>
